# Project Language Rule

The primary language for all documentation, code comments, commit messages, and communication in this project is **English**.

- All new files, pull requests, and issues should use English as the default language.
- This rule applies to README, code comments, documentation, and all project-related discussions.

This rule helps ensure consistency and accessibility for global contributors.
